  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into thin wedges</p><p>Peel thin strips of <strong>zest </strong>from your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> (avoid the white bitter pith)</p><p>Chop 2/3 of the <strong>red onion[s]</strong> into wedges, reserve the <strong>remaining red onion</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1715248270896-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1715248270896-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1715248270896-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1715248270896-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1715248270896-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> potato & onion wedges</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>dried oregano </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Add a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for an initial 20 min or until the potatoes have slightly browned</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1715248274067-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1715248274067-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1715248274067-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1715248274067-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1715248274067-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are in the oven, cut your <strong>heritage tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining red onion</strong> finely</p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> into quarters lengthways, then slice roughly</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1715248277310-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1715248277310-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
