          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1715248277310-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the juice from <strong>half</strong> the<strong> peeled</strong> <strong>lemon[s]</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to a bowl with 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [2 1/2 tbsp]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[3 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>sugar </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>lemon</strong> <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1715248280776-x200.jpg",
