            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped cucumber</strong>, <strong>sliced onion</strong>, your <strong>black olives</strong> and <strong>chopped heritage tomatoes</strong> to the dressing</p><p>Crumble your <strong>feta</strong> in roughly, add your <strong>remaining dried oregano</strong> and toss – this is your <strong>Greek-style</strong> <strong>salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
